reviewText:
This video is a must for those who want to know the history of Taliesin, it's resident students (the fellowship), its owner Mr. & Mrs. Frank Lloyd Wright and what its history means and especially to the present and future of the architectural realms.
I highly recommend owning it and even showing it to future clients of yours. It will enthuse them about the possibilities in our world and that ANYTHING is possible. My quote: "think about design and he (Frank Lloyd Wright)will come"
